Contains the example Message of the Day OSGi and REST service bundles.

- Installation
==============

On Karaf;

> features:chooseurl cxf 2.7.5
> features:install http cxf
> install -s mvn:org.safehaus.kiskis.mgmt/motd-api/0.0.1-SNAPSHOT
> install -s mvn:org.safehaus.kiskis.mgmt/motd-impl/0.0.1-SNAPSHOT
> install -s mvn:org.safehaus.kiskis.mgmt/motd-client/0.0.1-SNAPSHOT
> install -s mvn:org.safehaus.kiskis.mgmt/motd-rest/0.0.1-SNAPSHOT

- Test
======

http://localhost:8181/cxf/rest/motd

